snippet.title: Amiga Longplay: Hell Bent
snippet.description:
Destroy enough and fly to the exit. This is not so easy as it looks. There are a lot of enemies on screen trying to kill you. And they are impossible to avoid. And the fuel is running out very quickly, so you need to pick up energy and fuel all the time.

Longplay requested by: Valaxuna
